<section id="overview">
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>Apply <code>data-clip</code> to <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> or <code>&lt;figure&gt;</code> elements to mask them into responsive shapes. All shapes use percentage-based coordinates, so they scale with the element size. <code>object-fit: cover</code> is automatically enforced on clipped images.</p>
</section>

